Independently implemented. The concept of providing programmatic access to
NSFC's public project query was inspired by:
  - suqingdong/nsfc (https://github.com/suqingdong/nsfc, public)

This implementation does not contain code copied from the above project.
HTTP endpoints used are public NSFC web pages (kd.nsfc.cn, www.nsfc.gov.cn).
Users must comply with NSFC's terms of use and robots.txt.
